revision.text: == Possible Hints == Due to inconvenience, some berries cannot be selected as hints. Any Gen 3 or 4 berry can be selected, except the following: * Parasitic berries ([[File:Occa.png|15px]] [[Occa]], [[File:Kebia.png|15px]] [[Kebia]] or [[File:Colbur.png|15px]] [[Colbur]]) * Berries that prevent mutation ([[File:Babiri.png|15px]] [[Babiri]])
